org.mozilla.jss.tests

Class BadSSL

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mozilla.jss.tests.BadSSL

  • public class BadSSL
extends java.lang.Object
    The BadSSL test case maintains an internal mapping from badssl.com subdomains to expected exceptions and validates they occur. Since badssl.com offers no guaranteed SLA or availability, we likely shouldn't add this site to automated tests.
